H0.text: What was Blondie's last UK No 1 of the 80s. Atomic

H1.text: What was Blondie's last UK No 1 of the 80s. Call Me

H2.text: What was Blondie's last UK No 1 of the 80s. The Tide Is High

H3.text: What was Blondie's last UK No 1 of the 80s. Rapture

A4.text: The Tide Is High became Blondie's last UK number one for 18 years, until 'Maria' in February 1999.

A5.text: Atomic Kitten covered 'The Tide Is High' and released it as the second single from their second studio album, Feels So Good (2002), on 26 August 2002.
